Aktif skill motoru eklendi: Source-X CCharSkill.cpp pre-check, emote ve mesaj zinciri 13 skillde (Hiding/DetectingHidden/Meditation/SpiritSpeak/Begging/Healing/Stealing/Snooping/Lockpicking/RemoveTrap/Taming/Herding/Poisoning/Tracking) birebir port edildi. IActiveSkillSink, GameClient'a NpcSpeech tabanli Emote, PacketSound, backpack item arama/tuketim ve target cursor akisi olarak baglandi; SkillHandlers dispatcher hangi skill'in target istedigini ActiveSkillTargetKind ile bildirir.

Active-skill engine added: Source-X CCharSkill.cpp pre-check, emote, and message chain ported one-to-one for 13 skills (Hiding/DetectingHidden/Meditation/SpiritSpeak/Begging/Healing/Stealing/Snooping/Lockpicking/RemoveTrap/Taming/Herding/Poisoning/Tracking). IActiveSkillSink wires GameClient with NpcSpeech-based Emote, PacketSound, backpack lookup/consume, and a target-cursor flow; SkillHandlers dispatcher reports each skill's target requirement via ActiveSkillTargetKind.
